name: People of Crypto #002 - Vitalik Buterin
description:
PoC #002 - Vitalik Buterin.
Buterin is a wonder boy in crypto world. In 2013, he wrote a famouse whitepaper, soon-to-be Ethereum Network. Dubbed as "World Computer", many innovations and trends came from this network. The cons, traffic is much worse than any of third world country and extremely expensive network usage fee, commonly known as "Gas Fee".

16 Editions minted on Sept,27th 2021. Will burn all remaining unsold on Oct,11st 2021
